        "## 4. Memory Initialization\n",
        "\n",
        "A **sliding-window buffer** that retains the last 10 conversation turns.\n",
        "`return_messages=True` ensures history is returned as structured message objects\n",
        "(used by `format_chat_history` downstream).\n",
        "\n",
        "Memory is initialized here — **before** any node or chain references it.\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "store = {}\n",
        "\n",
        "def get_session_history(session_id: str):\n",
        "    if session_id not in store:\n",
        "        store[session_id] = InMemoryChatMessageHistory()\n",
        "\n",
        "    history = store[session_id]\n",
        "\n",
        "    if len(history.messages) > 20:\n",
        "        history.messages = history.messages[-20:]\n",
        "\n",
        "    return history"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "eKZkTD1lumVr"
      },
